original: Östberg, Karl Jacob Henrik, komminister, SolVesta, f. ’21/3/81 i Hjorted, Kalm. 1., av Jacob Ö. o. Axeline Åker- halm. G. 10 m. Elsa Widell Barn: Ingemar f. 11. — Mog:ex. i Linköp. 98, fil. kand. 03’, teol. kand. 06, prakt, teol. prov samt prästv. f. Linköp. stift 07. Tjg. s. past:adj. i Västra Eneby samt tf. kommin. o. v. pastor i Gammalkil, kommin. i Hannäs sed. 20. Ordf. i kyrkostämma o. skolstyr.
translated: Östberg, Karl Jacob Henrik, vicar, SolVesta, b. 21/3/81 in Hjorted, Kalm. 1., son of Jacob Ö. and Axeline Åkerhalm. Married in 10 to Elsa Widell. Children: Ingemar b. 11. — Completed studies in Linköping in 98, Bachelor of Arts in 03', Bachelor of Theology in 06, practical theology examination and ordained in Linköping diocese in 07. Currently serving as assistant pastor in Västra Eneby and temporary vicar and acting pastor in Gammalkil, vicar in Hannäs since 20. Chairman of church assembly and school board.
